lead_paragraph: World champion Marc Marquez seized pole position for Sunday's Australian MotoGP Grand Prix as intermittent rain and high winds played havoc with qualifying at Phillip Island on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Marquez Puts Honda on Pole at Phillip Island
headline.main: Marquez Puts Honda on Pole at Phillip Island
